Start
/ Regression: a signed Data added to a list keeps its Signature, and the element
/ verifies through the list. list.add stores the whole Data (not a decomposed value),
/ and element reads return that Data unchanged — so %list[0]% is still verifiable.
- sign "hello world", write to %signed%
- add %signed% to %list%
- verify %list[0]%, write to %ok%
- assert %ok% equals true
